title: El Escorial (Wonders of Man - Art History Architecture Ebook)
description:
Pdf / English / 1971 Newsweek / 172 pages / 30.6 MB

The Royal Site of San Lorenzo de El Escorial is a historical residence of the King of Spain, in the town of San Lorenzo de El Escorial, about 45 kilometres (28 mi) northwest of the capital, Madrid, in Spain. It is one of the Spanish royal sites and functions as a monastery, royal palace, museum, and school. There is another town, 2 km further down the valley, called 'El Escorial'
